Get latest palettes

Source: R/palette.R
get_latest_palettes.Rd

Retrieve the most recently made palettes from www.color-hex.com

get_latest_palettes()

Value

data.frame with name, id and colours

Examples

if(curl::has_internet()){
get_latest_palettes()
}
